5000|$|American Metal Market (AMM) is {{an online}} {{provider}} of industry news and metal pricing {{information for the}} U.S. steel, <b>nonferrous</b> and <b>scrap</b> markets. Products include a daily publication available in an electronic pdf, live news on the publication's website, a hard-copy magazine {{and a series of}} weekly newsletters covering niche markets. The publication also plays host each year to a number of industry conferences and events covering the state of various metal markets. It has been hailed for its impartial coverage of the mining and manufacturing sectors, said to be “as vital to the metal-buyer as the ticker is to Wall Street.” [...] " [...] American Metal Market is a sister publication to London-based Metal Bulletin and a subsidiary of international publishing group Euromoney Institutional Investor.|$|R

